*** MemoServ Help - Command: SET ***
Sets various memo-related options. You must be identified
to your nickname in order to use this command.
 
Syntax:
/ms SET OPTION parameters
 
Available options:
 
    IGNORETYPE - Set usage of your Memo Ignore List.
    NOTIFY     - Decide when you will be notified about new memos.
 
For more information on a specific option, type: /ms HELP SET option
 
Type /join #IRCHelp for more information.
*** End of Help ***